joe cocker and leon russell create a hot roadshow joe cocker teams up with tulsa native leon russell and a cast of over forty for a concert tour , and what a party ! the live set contains a mix of russell compositions and blues/r & amp ; b/pop/rock standards , all performed with the feral intensity of a man possessed . it 's clear that the magic could n't last in this form , and it did n't , although cocker did go on to make many fine records , and even some great ones , after his jaunt with russell